      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Postponing the rollout is a risk to your timeline, but keeping the old system running as a shadow fallback is the most prudent immediate solution. You can keep your current operational instance active, running parallel to the new system, until the new model proves it can handle complex VIP requests flawlessly. This ensures zero service interruption while allowing the development team the time they need to patch the knowledge gaps.",
